gure 6). # The height setting was a bit annoying. So you have to set the plotOut height as auto and then create a function inside render plot to set it to a value you want. renderPlot({ plotOutput(plotDecisionBoundary(X = X, y = y, lambda = input$lambda, initialTheta = initialTheta), height = &quot;auto&quot;) }, height = function() { 600 })
